of the evil soul.

277
00:13:51,197 --> 00:13:55,301
No, get away from me, let me go!

278
00:13:55,301 --> 00:13:57,437
We're all gonna
suffer Moo's fate!

279
00:13:57,437 --> 00:14:01,374
I don't wanna change, I like
myself just the way I am now!

280
00:14:01,374 --> 00:14:02,909
‐Oh no!
‐Unhand me!

281
00:14:02,909 --> 00:14:05,712
Why are you trying
to control my mind?

282
00:14:05,712 --> 00:14:08,348
(screaming)

283
00:14:08,348 --> 00:14:11,284
♪

284
00:14:11,284 --> 00:14:13,186
The evil soul is trying
to take possession

285
00:14:13,186 --> 00:14:15,621
of the souls of those
pitiful monsters.

286
00:14:15,621 --> 00:14:17,690
So that must mean
it's brought us here

287
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:19,392
to do the same thing to us.

288
00:14:19,392 --> 00:14:21,260
How do we stop it
from taking over?

289
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:23,930
We must use what the
evil soul despises.

290
00:14:23,930 --> 00:14:27,233
That's love and courage, and
the kind of strong determination

291
00:14:27,233 --> 00:14:29,669
to never give
into any obstacles.

292
00:14:29,669 --> 00:14:31,704
‐Courage.
‐Mhm.

293
00:14:31,704 --> 00:14:34,240
♪

294
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,909
