Phoenix's body anymore.

296
00:14:40,546 --> 00:14:43,549
Wait a sec, if we're inside
the evil soul's heart,

297
00:14:43,549 --> 00:14:46,018
then this place is imaginary
and we don't need a body.

298
00:14:46,018 --> 00:14:49,355
‐We just need to concentrate.
‐We can become Phoenix.

299
00:14:49,355 --> 00:14:51,691
That's right, we can do it!

300
00:14:51,691 --> 00:14:53,459
Let's pool our
courage and destroy

301
00:14:53,459 --> 00:14:55,495
