302
00:14:55,495 --> 00:15:32,832
♪

303
00:15:32,832 --> 00:15:35,968
(screeching)

304
00:15:35,968 --> 00:15:37,637
Go for it!

305
00:15:37,637 --> 00:15:48,514
♪

306
00:15:48,514 --> 00:15:49,749
What is that?

307
00:15:49,749 --> 00:15:51,617
I thought that
was just a legend.

308
00:15:51,617 --> 00:15:54,086
‐It's the Phoenix!
‐Impossible!

309
00:15:54,086 --> 00:15:56,722
They've become the
Phoenix to save us?

310
00:15:56,722 --> 00:15:58,858
Let Durahan and the others go!

311
00:15:58,858 --> 00:16:27,153
♪

312
00:16:27,153 --> 00:16:28,788
Don't give up!

313
00:16:28,788 --> 00:16:30,423
You can do it!

314
00:16:30,423 --> 00:16:45,371
♪

315
00:16:45,371 --> 00:16:47,707
The evil soul is trying
to possess the Phoenix!

316
00:16:47,707 --> 00:16:50,076
Don't give up, Phoenix!

317
00:16:50,076 --> 00:16:58,751
♪

318
00:16:58,751 --> 00:17:00,887
Our enemies are
fighting to save us.

319
00:17:00,887 --> 00:17:03,189
They're putting everything
on the line for us.

320
00:17:03,189 --> 00:17:05,958
I don't understand,
how can they do that?

321
00:17:05,958 --> 00:17:07,059
Yeah.

322
00:17:07,059 --> 00:17:09,128
I promise you,

323
00:17:09,128 --> 00:17:11,197
you'll never defeat us.

324
00:17:11,197 --> 00:17:15,067
Pool your courage
together, everybody!

325
00:17:15,067 --> 00:17:18,271
(shouting)

326
00:17:18,271 --> 00:17:38,057
♪

327
00:17:38,057 --> 00:17:40,426
Their love is outshining
the evil hatred.

328
00:17:40,426 --> 00:17:43,329
And that love is
strengthened by courage.

329
00:17:43,329 --> 00:17:46,432
They have the courage to
withstand any obstacles.

330
00:17:46,432 --> 00:17:49,902
The most vulnerable path
is the hardest one to follow,

331
00:17:49,902 --> 00:17:52,705
and that is what makes
it the strongest.

332
00:17:52,705 --> 00:17:55,007
♪

333
00:17:55,007 --> 00:17:57,610
I understand now, and
I've made up my mind.

334
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:59,645
