00:18:12,358 --> 00:19:13,853
♪

342
00:19:13,853 --> 00:19:15,488
Father!

343
00:19:15,488 --> 00:19:19,592
♪

344
00:19:19,592 --> 00:19:23,329
‐I have my own body back again!
‐So do I.

345
00:19:23,329 --> 00:19:25,931
And our baddie emblems
have disappeared.

346
00:19:25,931 --> 00:19:28,000
‐Gobi!
‐Yeah!

347
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:31,070
(laughing)

348
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:34,006
It was your courage that
overcame the evil soul.

349
00:19:34,006 --> 00:19:36,142
Your courage is invincible.

350
00:19:36,142 --> 00:19:59,098
♪

